text: Prahins was a municipality of the district Jura-Nord vaudois in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. The former municipality of Prahins merged on 1 January 2012 into the municipality of Donneloye.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 21 December 2011 == References == ==Other websites== Category:2010s disestablishments in Switzerland Category:2012 disestablishments in Europe Category:Former municipalities of Vaud
